<%= content_for :page_header do %>
    <span style="border: none;font-size: 40px;font-weight: bold;vertical-align: middle;text-align: left;width: 130px;color: white">DocuMentor</span>

<% end %>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span10">
    <h1>Documentation made easy</h1>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6">
        Credit Administration is a function at most banks and financial institutions,
        which provides multiple services to various businesses and across a wide spectrum of clients.
        The core engine of the business of finance, you will need to interact with them to close any and all deals you
        strike with your clients.

        <br/>
        <br/>
        So we decided to create for you a tool that will help you understand various legal / operation documents and
        processes.
        It is specifically designed keeping in mind your busy and mobile work-life, and targeted to allow you to learn
        at your pace and in your own time.
        With this and your co-operation, we hope your firm realizes the path to improved TATs, lower costs, higher
        efficiencyÂ and through it all, customer delight.

        <br/>
        <br/>
        <br/>

        <span style="font-size: 20px">Help us help you better...</span><br/>

        <br/>
        <br/>

      </div>
      <div class="span3">
        <br/>
        <% if !current_user %>
            <div style="text-align: right;color: #556b2f;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-right: 20px;">
              <a href="#" data-controls-modal="sign_up_form" data-backdrop="static" class="btn primary">Sign Up...</a>
            </div>
        <% else %>
            <div style="text-align: right;color: #556b2f;font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;margin-right: 20px;">
              <%= link_to "Enter >>", "#", :class=>"btn primary" %>
            </div>
        <% end %>
        <div id="sign_up_form" class="modal hide fade">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <a href="#" class="close"> &times; </a>

            <h3>Sign Up</h3>
          </div>

          <%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>

              <div class="modal-body">

                <div class="clearfix">
                  <%= f.label :email %>
                  <div class="input">  <%= f.email_field :email %></div>

                  <%= f.label :password %>
                  <div class="input">  <%= f.password_field :password %></div>

                  <%= f.label :re_enter %>
                  <div class="input">  <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation %></div>
                  <%= f.label :admin %>
                  <div class="input">  <%= f.check_box :admin %></div>

                </div>

              </div>


              <div class="modal-footer">

                <div>
                  <%= f.submit "Sign up", :class=>"btn error" %>
                </div>
              </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="span4">
    <table>
      <tr style="border: none;">
        <td style="border: none;">
          <%= image_tag("mind_map.jpg", :size => "64x64") %>
        </td>
        <td style="border: none;">
          Built on an Exploration based Training Structure
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <%= image_tag("system.png", :size => "64x64") %>
        </td>
        <td>
          Access it from anywhere as a Reference Guide
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <%= image_tag("quiz.jpg", :size => "70x70") %>
        </td>
        <td>
          Practical quizzes where you actually check docs online
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <%= image_tag("knowledge.jpg", :size => "70x70") %>
        </td>
        <td>
          Understand Credit Concepts, Products and Documents
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

